<div class='home-page'>
  <div class="landing">
    <div class="landing-content">
      <h1>Make it easier to <span class="highlighted-word">Map Out</span> your <span class="highlighted-word">Future</span></h1>
      <p id="landing-text-line">By gathering knowledge from experienced professionals, we provide unique insight to young people looking for their place in the world.</p>

      <div class="landing-buttons">
        <%= link_to new_mentor_path do %>
          <button class="button fill">
            Share your insight
          </button>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to dashboard_path do %>
          <button class="button border">
            Get started
          </button>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing-data-grid">
      <div class="landing-data-box left">
        <h2><strong>12</strong></h2>
        <p>The average number of times a person will change jobs/careers in their lifetime</p>
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfipoufmj/image/upload/v1687360557/pexels-andrea-piacquadio-3778966_unl4mq.jpg" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="landing-data-box-right">
        <div class="landing-data-box">
          <h3><strong class="highlighted-word">39%</strong></h3>
          <p>of students are over the age of 25.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="landing-data-box">
          <h3><strong class="highlighted-word">1 in every 2</strong></h3>
          <p>people work in a field totally unrelated to their degree</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section one">
    <div class="our-mission">
      <div class="information">
        <div>
          <p>Our mission</p>
          <h2 class="subheader">To give all young people <span class="highlighted-word">access,</span> <span class="highlighted-word">awareness,</span> and the <span class="highlighted-word">ability</span> to map out their own future.</h2>
        </div>
        <p>We are expected to make significant life decisions at an early stage, without having any real understanding of the opportunities available. Our solution is focused on bringing together individuals, personalities, and experiences to help everyone thrive.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card" id="card-01">
          <h3>Our Algorithm</h3>
          <p>Character traits signifcantly impact the decisions we make. We've developed a unique tool to match similar individuals based on personality, allowing you to discover new and bespoke pathways.</p>
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfipoufmj/image/upload/v1687270773/pexels-antonio-batinic%CC%81-4164418_e3ynog.jpg" alt="">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='cards-right'>
          <div class="card" id="card-02">
            <div class="card-data">
              <h3>Established professionals</h3>
              <p>Our community of professionals are here to help in any way they can. They were once in your shoes and are more than happy to impart their secrets to success.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfipoufmj/image/upload/v1686920328/pexels-kampus-production-5940841_rokpmx.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card" id="card-03">
            <div class="card-data">
              <h3>Browse</h3>
              <p>Scroll with a difference. Lets face it, traditional career sites and job boards offer little perspective on what life really looks like.
              To inspire your next steps, we have a library of real and honest accounts to help you understand what the future may hold.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfipoufmj/image/upload/v1686920324/pexels-fauxels-3184418_tzhnvq.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="home-page-span">
  <div class="section-two">
    <div class="section-two-left">
      <h2>Our Process</h2>
      <p>Designed to take you from clueless and overwhelmed, to focused, motivated, and informed.</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="section-two-right">
      <li class="stage">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-lightbulb"></i>
        <div>
          <h3>Take our questionnaire</h3>
          <p>Answer our questions honestly, there are no right or wrong answers. We want to know a little bit about you.</p>
        </div>
        <%= link_to new_questionnaire_path do %>
          <button class="button">
            Go To Questionnaire
          </button>
        <% end %>
      </li>
      <li class="stage">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-book-open"></i>
        <div>
          <h3>Browse our library</h3>
          <p>Explore and read about the experiences of others.</p>
        </div>
        <%= link_to profiles_path do %>
          <button class="button">
            Browse
          </button>
        <% end %>
      </li>
      <li class="stage">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-comments"></i>
        <div>
          <h3>Contact</h3>
          <p>If you want to find out more, we can help you. Many of our members are more than happy to answer any questions you may have.</p>
        </div>
        <%= link_to new_enquiry_path do %>
          <button class="button">
            Contact
          </button>
        <% end %>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="home-page">
  <div class="section four">
    <div class="become-a-member-container">
      <div class="member-image">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfipoufmj/image/upload/v1688378925/pexels-christina-morillo-1181722_dv9ogw.jpg" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="member-content">
        <div class="member-text">
          <h3>Ready to share?</h3>
          <p>Be a part of our mission to inspire young people by registering with us below. No matter how advanced you are in your field, you can help positively impact young lives.</p>
          <div class="button-container">
            <%= link_to "Join as a professional", new_mentor_path, class: "button become-a-member-button" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
